## ğŸ§© Extending the Framework
- Add new datasets in `src/langtune/data/datasets.py`
- Add new callbacks in `src/langtune/callbacks/`
- Add new models in `src/langtune/models/`
- Add new CLI tools in `src/langtune/cli/`

